<br>
The agros that are hard to quantify are debuffs like slow, snare, tash, etc. that have no damage component.  The other aspect that's hard to quantify is the tendency for the most recent damage to be placed higher on the agro list -- ie. the reason why lower DPS dual-wielding configurations actually taunt better than higher DPS 2H rigs.  If we could look at the code, we could know for sure, but Sony isn't forthcoming with that information.  Anyway, disembowler is a bit faster and thus I'd guess it would likely also help you keep agro better than frostbringer.<br>
<br>
